lead_paragraph: Inter Milan may have made a disappointing start to the Serie A season but they are one of Lazio's chief rivals in the race for a Champions League slot, according to the Roman side's coach Simone Inzaghi.

headline.print_headline: Inter Big Rivals for Lazio's European Ambitions-Inzaghi
